{"tid":1374682,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"（講ACG唔講政治）外國勢力：「黑景」","createTime":"2019-07-27T23:23:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T10:00:40.000Z","uid":247977,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"21f1e1951f0d4e7956ae0ab3e69ac776e181b7b8","tid":1374682,"uid":247977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T23:23:38.000Z","msg":"見呢兩日大家都講元朗動漫展咁開心，我都Po下前一兩個月我在澳洲兩個動漫展影的相<br />\n<br />\n講明唔講政治的！歡迎踩我的Sony相，膚色好乜都好<br />\n<br />\n由於我不滿個場地無乜好背景，所以就算日頭白色底都好（有一半相係黑底背景），我都打燈當睇唔到，打個「黑景」出黎。反正白色的睇唔到就無事<br />\n(真係日光日白當Studio黑景黎影😈😈 真係唔講政治的）<br />\n<br />\n澳洲動漫同人展規模遠比唔上香港的（更唔好講日本台灣），但有個好的地方係佢地唔會當燈腳係武器。如果唔係我本來打算用籐條黎做燈腳的😫😫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後講多次，我真係Po動漫相的，唔會有委任證，更唔會對住老人院放催淚彈！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pyV6ZiE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpyV6ZiE.jpg&h=aea2e2b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/08vuW5m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F08vuW5m.jpg&h=9390b94d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pKdo1w4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpKdo1w4.jpg&h=1f990681&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o9LuW5s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo9LuW5s.jpg&h=a8b6e2df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3iD8tca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3iD8tca.jpg&h=2cae1b71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P66RqYU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP66RqYU.jpg&h=d4535e9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/efecaqC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FefecaqC.jpg&h=f4fec6e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LTTXmxm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLTTXmxm.jpg&h=2e4d8